/li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9A%E8%AF%B4%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9-4-%E9%81%93%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8E%E6%9C%AC%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C-%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A2%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC4%E3%80%818%E3%80%817%E3%80%819-%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88-%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%83%E5%9D%87-%E2%89%A0-%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第5题：说选项 4 道题中有一题的答案与本题的答案相同， 线索是第4、8、7、9 题中有一题的答案 &#x3D; 第5题的答案，其它均 ≠ 第5题的答案；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9A%E8%AF%B4%E4%BB%85%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%A4%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC8%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A2%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC-2-4-%E3%80%81-1-6-%E3%80%81-3-10-%E3%80%81-5-9-%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%BB%84%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E7%AC%AC8%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%83%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC8%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第6题：说仅有两题与第8题相同，线索是第(2,4) 、(1,6) 、(3,10)、 (5,9) 题中有一组等于第8题，其它与第8题不同；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC7%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%89%E4%B8%AD%E6%AC%A1%E6%95%B0%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%91%EF%BC%8C%E6%AC%A1%E6%95%B0%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E6%89%8D%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%88%E4%B8%8D%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%AE%83%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第7题：选中次数最少，次数需要统计，应该是最后才知道结果的，现在先不考虑它；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC8%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B8%E9%82%BB%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A2%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC-2%E3%80%815%E3%80%817%E3%80%8110-%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%893%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC1%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D%E7%9B%B8%E9%82%BB%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第8题：与第一题的答案字母不相邻，线索是第 2、5、7、10 题中有3题答案与第1题答案字母相邻；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC9%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%A4%E6%9D%A1%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E8%AF%AD%E5%8F%A5%E7%9C%9F%E5%81%87%E6%80%A7%E7%9B%B8%E5%8F%8D%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A2%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC9%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%A4%E5%8F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%A5%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%A5%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%81%87%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第9题：两条逻辑语句真假性相反，线索是第9题两句中有一句肯定是真的，另一句肯定是假的；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC10%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9A%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E6%AC%A1%E6%95%B0%E5%B7%AE%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E6%89%8D%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%89%8D%E9%9D%A2%E4%B9%9F%E5%85%88%E4%B8%8D%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%AE%83%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第10题：出现次数差，也需要统计，应该也是最后才知道结果，前面也先不考虑它。</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%87%E4%B8%80%E8%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A2%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">经过一轮的简单分析后，我们得到如下线索：</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A21%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC2%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">线索1：第2题和第5题答案不相同；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A22%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC2%E3%80%813%E3%80%814%E3%80%816-%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%893%E4%B8%AA%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">线索2：第2、3、4、6 题中有3个答案相同；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A23%EF%BC%9A-1-5-%E3%80%81-2-7-%E3%80%81-1-9-%E3%80%81-6-10-%E8%BF%99%E5%9B%9B%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%BB%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">线索3：(1,5)、 (2,7) 、(1,9)、 (6,10) 这四组中有一组答案相同；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A24%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC4%E3%80%817%E3%80%818%E3%80%819-%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%83%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">线索4：第4、7、8、9 题中有一题和第5题答案相同，其它与第5题不同；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A25%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC-2-4-%E3%80%81-1-6-%E3%80%81-3-10-%E3%80%81-5-9-%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%BB%84%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC8%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%83%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC8%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">线索5：第 (2,4)、 (1,6) 、(3,10) 、(5,9) 题中有一组和第8题答案相同，其它与第8题不同；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A26%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC2%E3%80%815%E3%80%817%E3%80%8110-%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%893%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC1%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E5%AD%97%E6%AF%8D%E7%9B%B8%E8%BF%9E%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">线索6：第2、5、7、10 题中有3题答案与第1题答案字母相连；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A27%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC9%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%A4%E5%8F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%A5%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%A5%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%81%87%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">线索7：第9题两句中有一句肯定是真的，另一句肯定是假的；</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%87%E6%95%B4%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C-%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E7%AC%AC7%E6%9D%A1%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A2%E7%BB%99%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E9%82%A3%E4%B9%88%E4%B8%80%E7%9C%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%81%87%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E4%B8%A4%E6%AC%A1%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE%E5%8D%B3%E5%8F%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E4%BB%8E%E7%AC%AC7%E6%9D%A1%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A2%E5%B1%95%E5%BC%80%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">经过整理， 我们发现第7条线索给出的是一个逻辑判断的条件，那么一真一假之间，只需要最多验证两次假设即可，所以我们选择从第7条线索展开思考。</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A27%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">分析线索7：</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E2%80%9C%E7%AC%AC1%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E2%80%9D-%E4%B8%8E-%E2%80%9C%E7%AC%ACX%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E2%80%9D-%E4%B8%A4%E5%8F%A5%E8%AF%9D%E7%9A%84%E7%9C%9F%E5%81%87%E6%80%A7%E7%9B%B8%E5%8F%8D%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E8%AF%B4%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%A4%E5%8F%A5%E8%AF%9D%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%80%E7%9C%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%81%87%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">“第1题与第6题的答案相同” 与 “第X题与第5题的答案相同” 两句话的真假性相反，也就是说这两句话“一真一假”。</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%88%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE%E2%80%9C%E7%AC%AC1%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E2%80%9D%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">先假设“第1题与第6题的答案相同”是真的。</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%82%A3%E4%B9%88%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E6%89%BE%E5%87%BA%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E2%80%9C%E7%AC%ACX%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E2%80%9D%E8%BF%99%E5%8F%A5%E8%AF%9D%E6%98%AF%E5%81%87%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%81%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%ACX%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">那么我们需要找出满足“第X题与第5题的答案相同”这句话是假的证据，也就是第X题和第5题答案不相同。</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E6%98%AF%E5%8D%95%E9%80%89%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E5%8F%AA%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%83%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">因为是单选题的原因，选项中应该只存在一个答案不相同，其它三个答案应该都与第5题相同。</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E4%B8%8A%E9%9D%A2%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A21%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E7%AC%AC2%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E9%82%A3%E4%B9%88%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%83%E7%AC%AC1%E3%80%816%E3%80%819%E3%80%8110-%E9%A2%98%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">根据上面线索1判断，只有第2题答案不等于第5题，那么其它第1、6、9、10 题都是和第5题答案相同。</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BF%99%E6%97%B6%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E8%BF%9D%E8%83%8C%E4%BA%86%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A23%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A23%E4%B8%AD%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E7%BB%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF-1-9-%E3%80%81-6-10-%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">这时我们发现这个结果违背了线索3，线索3中应该只有一组答案相同，但是(1,9) 、(6,10) 都是相同的。</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%82%A3%E4%B9%88%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%93%E8%AE%BA%E6%98%AF%E2%80%9C%E7%AC%AC1%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E2%80%9C%E7%AC%ACX%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8E%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E2%80%9D%E6%98%AF%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">那么最后结论是“第1题与第6题的答案相同”的假设不成立，而“第X题与第5题的答案相同”是成立的。</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8CX%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AFC%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A21%E4%B8%AD%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E4%BA%86%E7%AC%AC2%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">这里X肯定不是C，因为线索1中确定了第2题和第5题答案不相同。</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8CX%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AFD%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E7%AC%AC9%E9%A2%98%E8%8B%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%99%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E6%98%AFC%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%88%E6%98%8E%E6%98%BED%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E9%94%99%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">这里X肯定也不是D，因为第9题若是和第5题相同，则第5题答案是C，很明显D也是错的。</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A2%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">增加线索：</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A28%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC1%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">线索8：第1题和第6题答案不相同；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A29%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC9%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">线索9：第9题和第5题答案不相同；</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">继续分析：</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8CX%E8%82%AF%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AFA%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E5%81%87%E8%AE%BE%E6%98%AFA%E5%88%99%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%8E%A8%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">这里X肯定也不是A，因为假设是A则第5题和第6题答案相同，就可以推论：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AFA%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%BA%E7%AC%AC2%E3%80%814%E3%80%815%E3%80%818%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E9%83%BD%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E8%BF%9D%E8%83%8C%E4%BA%86%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A21%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第5题和第6题答案都是A时：结果为第2、4、5、8题答案都相同，显示违背了线索1，不成立；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AFB%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9B%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%9D%E8%83%8C%E4%BA%86%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A28%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第5题和第6题答案都是B时：第6题的选项B已经违背了线索8，不成立；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AFC%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9C%E5%B0%B1%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%9D%E8%83%8C%E4%BA%86%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A29%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第5题和第6题答案都是C时：第5题选择C就已经违背了线索9，不成立；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AFD%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9D%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%9D%E8%83%8C%E4%BA%86%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A29%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第5题和第6题答案都是D时：第6题的选项D已经违背了线索9，不成立；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5X%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AFB-%E7%AC%AC10%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">所以X的结果是B.第10题。</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A2%EF%BC%9A-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">增加线索：</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BA%BF%E7%B4%A210%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC5%E9%A2%98%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC10%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">线索10：第5题和第10题答案相同；</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC9%E9%A2%98%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%BE%97%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E7%AC%AC1%E4%B8%AA%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第9题分析完成，我们得出了第1个确定的答案：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC9%E9%A2%98%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%9AB%EF%BC%9B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第9题答案：B；</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%86%8D%E6%9D%A5%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9A%EF%BC%88%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E7%AC%AC6%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%83%E7%BB%99%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E8%B6%8A%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E6%89